# Source Packages
#
# Place source packages in subdirectories here. Each subdirectory
# should contain one of:
#
#   - Makefile        -> make && make DESTDIR=$ROOTFS install
#   - CMakeLists.txt  -> cmake build and install to /usr
#   - setup.py / pyproject.toml -> pip install
#   - install.sh      -> bash install.sh $ROOTFS
#
# Example structure:
#   packages/source/
#     my-daemon/
#       Makefile
#       src/
#       include/
#     my-tool/
#       install.sh
#
# You can also specify source packages from outside this directory
# using INCLUDE_SOURCE_PKGS in oniecraft.conf.
